In the above files you will find programs related to condition statement and loops where the syntax for the same is shown . Syntax is basically they way in which you will write certain things. You can compare it to grammar of certain language.
In condition statement we have statements such as if, if else, switch , etc which helps us to optimize our programs 
In loops we have for loop for, while, do while, etc which helps us in repeating a certain task without writing it again and again
